## DESCRIPTION
##   Arrange statements for a proof in proper order
## ENDDESCRIPTION


## DBsubject(Set theory and logic)
## DBchapter(Relations between sets)
## DBsection(Subset)
## Date(Summer 2013)
## Institution(Mississippi College)
## Author(John Travis)
## Level(3)
